     Modern frosted glass effects with depth
     
     Accessibility & Performance Features:
     - All glass effects respect prefers-reduced-motion media query
     - Automatic performance optimization for mobile devices
     - Proper focus states and ARIA attributes
     - High contrast mode support
     - Reduced motion support for accessibility
     ======================================== */
  
  /* Consistent Animation Timing and Easing System */
  .animate-ease-default {
    transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1); /* easeInOut */
  }
  
